description:
My HoneyDew this week is YMH Producer Nadav Itzkowitz aka BlueBan! Nadav shares stories about ripping his lucky pair of pants, getting rejected on a ferris wheel, and getting rectally probed during a doctor's visit. He also discusses the time his Dad tried to convince his professor to fail him. All this and more in this week's episode of The Dew! Make sure you subscribe to my YouTube & be ready to watch The Dew there beginning June 1!
